Manage Media Database\
Description: manage books, games, shows, movies within the database and their attributes \
Actors: Manager, Database\
Pre-condition: Must be authentic Chimera Manager\
Triggers:\
Basic Flow: \
	1. Manager logins in to admin account and chooses the media database\
	2. Manger selects a category(books, shows, games, movies)\
	3. The system shows a list of tittles for the selected category \
	4. Manager can select titles to delete, edit, or add \
	5. If manager chooses a title to edit, the selected title is loaded  \
	6. Changes can be made to various attributes\
	7. The system updates the database and shows the changes \
Extensions:\
	1. Filter categories\
		1a. Manager selects a subcategory to filter\
		1b. The system a list of items matching the subcategory \
	2. Cancel changes\
		1a. After making changes to a title, manger clicks cancel button to undo\
		1b. System does no update\
